                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330704-55-victim621 t18330704-55-viclabel282"></join>. On the 9th of June, I was in <placeName id="t18330704-55-crimeloc283">Tabernacle-walk, near the City-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18330704-55-crimeloc283" type="placeName" value="Tabernacle-walk, near the City-road"></interp>
